FBIS4-36038 "drnes107_j_94029" FBIS-NES-94-107 Daily Report 2 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Al-Bid Makes Military Appointments Al-Bid Makes Military Appointments EA0206191594 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in English 1600 GMT 2 Jun 94 EA0206191594 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network in English 1600 GMT 2 Jun 94 English BFN [Text] Mr. 'Ali Salim al-Bid, the chairman of the Presidential Council yesterday issued three decrees of the Presidential Council. The first appointed Shaykh Ahmad Farid al-Sughaymah, the governor of Shabwah Governorate, as military and administrative commander of the coastal axis. The second decree appointed Salih Abu-Bakr Bin-Husaynun, member of the Central Committee, as military and administrative commander of the interior axis. The third decree appointed Mr. Muhammad Salim Ba Hudaylah as military and administrative commander of Daw'an-Irma axis.
